se.swedenconnect.opensaml.xmlsec.keyinfo

Class KeyAgreementKeyInfoGeneratorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opensaml.xmlsec.keyinfo.impl.BasicKeyInfoGeneratorFactory
      • org.opensaml.xmlsec.keyinfo.impl.X509KeyInfoGeneratorFactory
        • se.swedenconnect.opensaml.xmlsec.keyinfo.KeyAgreementKeyInfoGeneratorFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.opensaml.xmlsec.keyinfo.KeyInfoGeneratorFactory

    public class KeyAgreementKeyInfoGeneratorFactory
extends org.opensaml.xmlsec.keyinfo.impl.X509KeyInfoGeneratorFactory
    Key info generator to be used when encrypting using key agreement methods.

    Note that either emitOriginatorKeyInfoPublicKeyValue or emitOriginatorKeyInfoPublicDEREncodedKeyValue must be set. Otherwise, and empty OriginatorKeyInfo element will be created.

    Author:
    Martin Lindström (martin@idsec.se), Stefan Santesson (stefan@idsec.se)
